### 🔐 **[Category Name]**

<details>
<summary><strong>🛡️ [Project Name] - [Brief Description]</strong></summary>

**🎯 Problem Solved**: [What real-world problem this solves]

**💡 Key Features**:
- [Feature 1 with technical detail]
- [Feature 2 with technical detail]
- [Feature 3 with technical detail]
- [Feature 4 with technical detail]

**🛠 Tech Stack**: `Technology` `Technology` `Technology` `Technology`

**📈 Business Impact**: [How this demonstrates professional value]

</details>

<details>
<summary><strong>⚡ [Project Name] - [Brief Description]</strong></summary>

[Same structure as above]

</details>

### 🚀 **[Next Category]**

[Repeat expandable project structure]

---
```

